title: Gold II Mid Laner looking for jungler DuoQ
body:
Hey as you can see in the Title I am looking for a DuoQ Jungler.
I am currently Gold II main mid.
I am 17years old from germany.
I am a calm dude who loves doing some jokes :)

conditions - Age: 16-26
Elo: gold IV - platin V
Skype
You should be from the UK or Germany because my english is okay but I have some problems with accents :D

I am able to play:
in the week from 20.00 - 22.00 (german time)
at the weekend  20.00 - 01.00 (german time)

Contact me if you are interested 
ingame name : xXDelokXX

sorry if there are some faults in this text ^^'
